videos.description: Georgia Tech's Brandon Alston dishes the ball to Abdoulaye Gueye in the post for a hook shot finish.
videos.headline: Gueye converts hook shot in post

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie finds space behind the arc and converts a step-back 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Okogie knocks down step-back 3

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie takes it to the paint and converts a difficult lay-in.
videos.headline: Okogie sinks tough layup

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Tadiric Jackson drives inside and converts the tough layup to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Jackson nails layup for and-1 opportunity

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie finds Abdoulaye Gueye open down low for a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Okogie sets up Gueye's slam

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie finds Jose Alvarado in the corner for the contested jumper and foul, earning a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Alvarado sinks step-back jumper for and-1 chance

videos.description: Clemson's Marcquise Reed swings the ball over to Shelton Mitchell for a 3-pointer and a foul to earn a trip to the line for a 4-point chance.
videos.headline: Mitchell earns chance at 4-point play

videos.description: Clemson's Elijah Thomas gets the ball inside and sinks a layup to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Thomas converts tough lay-in for and-1 chance

videos.description: Georgia Tech alum Chris Bosh joins Cory Alexander and Anish Shroff to discuss his health and the transitions Georgia Tech has made since he last played there.
videos.headline: Bosh on health: 'I'm feeling great'

videos.description: Clemson's Marcquise Reed dishes the ball off to Gabe DeVoe on the break for a two-handed dunk, putting DeVoe at a career high 25 points.
videos.headline: Reed's steal sets up DeVoe's slam

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Abdoulaye Gueye dishes the ball out to Josh Okogie behind the arc for a 3-pointer late in the game.
videos.headline: Okogie drains clutch 3-pointer

videos.description: With the score even at 70, Clemson's Marcquise Reed drives down the paint and converts a clutch layup late in the second half.
videos.headline: Reed sinks go-ahead layup
